          "Stock Transfers"
        ],
        "summary": "Initiate Stock Transfer Approval",
        "description": "This operation initiates the approval process for a stock transfer between specified warehouse locations. The request requires unique identifiers for both the approval and the warehouses involved, along with the necessary information in the request body. Successfully processing the request will update the transfer status and provide the necessary approval confirmation.",
